#Required Parameters
mu 602.2141989999999
rho 602.2141989999999
KB 0.0083144721451
T 298.15
EulerianType Eulerian_Period #Only this type is supported.
LagrangianType Lagrangian_LAMMPS #Only this type is supported.
nsteps 1000000 #please remove the run and fixSELM statements from the LAMMPS input script.

#Optional Parameters
flagStochasticDriving 0 #If the parameter is not provided, the default value is 0.
SELM_Seed 123456 #If flagStochasticDriving is 1, but the SELM_Seed parameter is not provided, then SELM_Seed is initialized using the system's random seed.
numMeshPtsPerDir 30 30 30 #In this program, it is assumed that the DeltaX is the same in each dimension, therefore numMeshPtsPerDir should be the same in every dimension.
saveSkipSimulationData 30
writeParticalV 1
writeParticalX 1
writeParticalF 1
